---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 119
By: St Augustine
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=Suffering Inseparable From the
    Fallen State
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=The Descent Into Hell
---
A man who would enter Paradise must go through fire and water, whether he be
Peter, to whom the keys of heaven were entrusted, or Paul, a chosen vessel of
God.  or John, to whom all the secrets of God were revealed.
